The code in question from Turbolinks:

```javascript
reflectRedirectedUrl = function() {
    var location, preservedHash;
    if (location = xhr.getResponseHeader('X-XHR-Redirected-To')) {
      location = new ComponentUrl(location);
      preservedHash = location.hasNoHash() ? document.location.hash : '';
      return window.history.replaceState(window.history.state, '', location.href + preservedHash);
    }
  };
```

The `X-XHR-Redirected-To` field shows the internal Rails configuration unless special nginx configuration is used to mask this.
These settings are modeled after omnibus-gitlab.

